\c 16
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* izatshaya abakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 2 Ungazithatheli umfazi, njalo ungabi lamadodana kumbe amadodakazi kulindawo.
\v 3 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* mayelana lamadodana lamayelana lamadodakazi azalelwe kulindawo, lamayelana labonina abawazalayo lamayelana laboyise abawazalele kulelilizwe:
\v 4 Bazakufa izimfa zemikhuhlane;\x + 15.2.\x* kabayikulilelwa,\x + 16.6; 22.18,19; 25.33. Hez. 7.11.\x* futhi kabayikungcwatshwa;\x + 16.6. 22.18,19; 25.33. Hez. 7.11.\x* bazakuba ngumquba phezu kobuso bomhlaba;\x + 8.2.\x* njalo bazaqedwa\x + 14.12.\x* yinkemba\x + 15.2.\x* layindlala;\x + 15.2.\x* lezidumbu zabo zizakuba yikudla kwezinyoni zamazulu\x + 19.7; 34.20. Dute. 28.26.\x* lokwenyamazana zomhlaba.
\v 5 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ungangeni endlini yesililo,\x + Hez. 24.16,17,22,23.\x* ungayikulila, ungabakhaleli; ngoba ngikususile ukuthula kwami kulababantu, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, uthandolomusa lezihawu.
\v 6 Njalo abakhulu labancinyane bazakufa kulelilizwe; kabayikungcwatshwa,\x + 16.6; 22.18,19; 25.33. Hez. 7.11.\x* kabayikubalilela,\x + 16.6; 22.18,19; 25.33. Hez. 7.11.\x* kabayikuzisika,\x + Dute. 14.1. Levi 19.28.\x* kabayikuziphuca\x + Jobe 1.20. Isa. 3.24.\x* ngenxa yabo.
\v 7 Futhi kabayikubahlephulela \add isinkwa\add* esililweni, ukubaduduza ngenxa yofileyo; futhi kakho ozabanathisa inkezo yezinduduzo ngenxa kayise langenxa kanina.
\v 8 Njalo ungangeni endlini yedili, ukuhlala labo, ukudla lokunatha.
\v 9 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangelani, ngizakwenza ukuthi kuphele kule indawo, emehlweni enu,\x + 7.34.\x* lensukwini zenu, ilizwi lentokozo, lelizwi lenjabulo, ilizwi lomyeni, lelizwi likamakoti.
\p
\v 10 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho utshela lababantu wonke lamazwi, babesebesithi kuwe: IN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumelani konke lokhu okubi okukhulu imelene lathi,\x + 5.19. Dute. 29.24.\x* njalo buyini ububi bethu, njalo yisiphi isono sethu esisonileyo simelene leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu?
\v 11 Khona uzakuthi kubo:\x + 22.9. Dute. 29.25.\x* Ngenxa yokuthi oyihlo bangidelile, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, balandela abanye onkulunkulu,\x + 13.10.\x* babasebenzela, babakhonza, bangidela mina, kabagcinanga umlayo wami;
\v 12 lina-ke lenze okubi kulaboyihlo;\x + 7.26.\x* ngoba khangelani, lilandela, ngulowo lalowo ubulukhuni benhliziyo yakhe embi,\x + 13.10.\x* ukuthi bangangilaleli.
\v 13 Ngakho ngizaliphosela ngaphandle kwalelilizwe,\x + 10.18. Dute. 4.26-28; 28.36,63-65.\x*\x + 22.26. Isa. 22.17,18.\x* liye elizweni elingalaziyo,\x + 15.14; 17.4.\x* lina laboyihlo; lapho-ke lizasebenzela abanye onkulunkulu emini lebusuku, ngoba kangiyikulinika umusa.
\p
\v 14 Ngakho, khangela,\x + 16.15; 23.7,8. Isa. 43.18.\x* insuku ziyeza,\x + 9.25.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho kungasayikuthiwa: Kuphila kweN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 4.2.\x* eyakhuphula abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe;
\v 15 kodwa: Kuphila kweN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 4.2.\x* eyakhuphula abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni lenyakatho\x + 3.18. Isa. 43.5,6.\x* lakuwo wonke amazwe eyayibaxotshele kiwo; ngoba ngizababuyisa futhi elizweni lakibo engalinika oyise.\x + 24.6; 30.3; 32.37.\x*
\p
\v 16 Khangela, ngizathumela kubagoli benhlanzi\x + Hez. 12.13. Amos 4.2. Hab. 1.15.\x* abanengi, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, babesebebagola; lemva kwalokho ngizathumela kubazingeli abanengi, babazingele bebasusa kuyo yonke intaba, lakulo lonke uqaqa, lasezingoxweni zamadwala.\x + 13.4.\x*
\v 17 Ngoba amehlo ami aphezu kwazo zonke izindlela zabo;\x + 32.19. 2 Lan. 16.9.\x* kazifihlakalanga ebusweni bami, lobubi babo kabucatshanga phambi kwamehlo ami.\x + Hlab. 51.9; 90.8.\x*
\v 18 Kuqala-ke ngizaphindisela isiphambeko sabo lesono sabo\x + Isa. 65.6.\x* ngokuphindiweyo,\x + 17.18. Isa. 40.2.\x* ngoba bengcolise ilizwe lami,\x + 2.7; 3.1. Hez. 43.7,9.\x* bagcwalisa ilifa lami ngezidumbu zamanyala abo lezinengiso zabo.
\p
\v 19 N\nd kosi\nd*, wena mandla ami, lenqaba yami,\x + 2 Sam. 22.33. Hlab. 31.4; 43.2. Isa. 25.4; 27.5.\x* lesiphephelo sami ngosuku lwembandezelo,\x + 17.17. 2 Sam. 22.3.\x* abezizwe bazafika kuwe bevela emikhawulweni yomhlaba, bathi: Isibili obaba badlile ilifa lamanga, okuyize,\x + 2.5; 18.15.\x* lokungekho inzuzo kukho.\x + Isa. 44.10.\x*\x + 2.11.\x*
\v 20 Umuntu angazenzela onkulunkulu yini, kanti kabayisibo onkulunkulu?\x + 2.11.\x*
\v 21 Ngakho, khangela, ngizabenza bazi okwalesisikhathi,\x + 10.18.\x* ngizabenza bazi isandla sami lobuqhawe bami; bazakwazi-ke ukuthi ibizo lami linguJehova.\x + 33.2. Eks. 6.3; 15.3. Amos 4.13.\x*